data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Connerton Village, where resort-style living meets everyday luxury, where Landscape/Lawn maintenance is provided by the HOA. This stunning Taylor Morrison Kentwood III home, boasting 3,450 square feet, offers the perfect blend of spaciousness and elegance. With 5 bedrooms and 4 ½ bathrooms, including a convenient lower level guest bedroom with en-suite bath, this home is designed for comfort and convenience.  Step inside and discover a chef's paradise in the large gourmet kitchen, complete with an oversized granite island and seating for up to five. Whether you're hosting formal dinner parties or casual gatherings, the kitchen's layout is ideal for both. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a generous eat-in area, perfect for cozy family breakfasts or relaxed meals with friends.  The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen and great room, creating a fluid space that's perfect for entertaining. High ceilings adorned with exquisite trim work and coffered ceilings add a touch of sophistication to the expansive living area. The natural flow of the home extends outdoors, where you can enjoy the Florida sunshine in your private pool.  This home also features a rare bonus—an upstairs multipurpose room, providing you with endless possibilities for customization. Whether you envision a home office, a playroom, or a media center, this extra space allows you to tailor your home to your unique needs.  With freshly painted interiors and exteriors (completed in March 2023), this home is not only stunning but move-in ready, allowing you to settle in and start creating lifelong memories. The property is situated on a corner lot within the gated community of Gardenia Glen, adding an extra layer of privacy and security to your living experience.  Beyond the confines of your beautiful abode, Connerton Village beckons you to enjoy a vibrant community lifestyle. Dive into the refreshing waters of the community pool, explore the lush garden park, or take a leisurely stroll along the multiple trails. Connerton Village also offers multi-use ponds where you can indulge in non-motorized activities, fostering a sense of connection with nature. Lanscape/Lawn maintenance is provided by the HOA.
